Stay on 836 West and then use the right 3 lanes to merge onto FL-826 S. Keep left at the fork to continue on FL-874 S, follow signs for Toll Rd/Homestead. Merge onto Ronald Reagan Tpke. Take the Ronald Reagan Tpke to US-1 South. Continue on US-1 and Largo Resort will be on the right. From Fort Lauderdale-Hollywood International Airport ~ 1 hour 45 minute drive (89.4 miles) Get on I-595 W from Terminal Dr. Continue on I-595 W to Davie. Take exit 8-9A-9B from I-595 W.
Follow Florida’s Tpke and Ronald Reagan Tpke to US-1 S/NE 1st Ave in Florida City. Merge onto US-1 S/NE 1st Ave. Continue on US-1 and Largo Resort will be on the right.
